  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Changes to SPC and patent law if UK leaves the EU without a deal
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Changes to Supplementary Protection Certificates (SPCs) and patent law in the event of no deal from the European Union.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

